  <heading>UZPQ1</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>Concatenate even elements within each pair of quadword vector segments</brief>
    <description>
      <para>Concatenate adjacent even-numbered elements from the corresponding 128-bit vector segments of the first and second source vectors and place in elements of the corresponding destination vector segment. This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </description>
    <status>Green</status>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <uses_dit condition="FEAT_SVE2 is implemented or FEAT_SME is implemented">True</uses_dit>
  </desc>
